# EM32 Timer driver configuration

config TIMER_EM32
	bool "ELAN EM32 Timer driver"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_ELAN_EM32_TIMER_ENABLED
	help
	  Enable Timer driver for ELAN EM32 microcontroller family.

	  The EM32 Timer controller supports:
	  - 32-bit down counter with auto-reload
	  - Configurable prescaler (1, 16, 256)
	  - One-shot and periodic modes
	  - Interrupt generation on underflow
	  - System timer functionality


